Sentencas: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cell (DA-SOFC) is a promising device to realize high-efficiency NH3-to-power.
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: In this study, we fabricate a series of cobalt-based spinet ACo(2)O(4) (ACO, A = Zn, Fe, Ni) oxide as DA-SOFC cathodes using the citric acid complexing method.
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: We prepare three cobalt-based spine] oxides with different A-site elements, i.e., Zn, Fe, and Ni, to establish the relationships between the valence and active site of ACO spinel oxide.
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: The structural analysis based on XRD, XPS, TEC, and UV-Vis diffuse reflectance confirms that NCO exhibits smaller band gap, higher electronic conductivity, and better compatibility with electrolyte.
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: The electrochemical results indicate that the cathodic surface of NCO containing rich Co3+ and O-ads leads to better oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) activity.
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the DA-SOFC using NCO cathode reaches 1.06 W.cm(-2) at 800 degrees C, superior to those of using ZCO (0.83 W.cm(-2)) or FCO (0.92 W.cm(-2))
Titulo: Direct ammonia solid oxide fuel cells based on spinel ACo2O4 (A=Zn, Fe, Ni) composite cathodes at intermediate temperature
